==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Passionately
<hw>Pas"sion*ate*ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>In a passionate manner; with strong feeling; ardently.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Sorrow expresses itself . . . loudly and
<qex>passionately</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>South.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Angrily; irascibly.</def>
<rj><au>Locke.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Passionateness</ent>⟦br⟧
